### 1. Register
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alex",
  "email": "alex@test.com",
  "password": "secret123",
  "displayName": "Alex"
}

###

### 2. Login (copy the token from the response)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alex@test.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

###

### 3. Create environment (paste your token below)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/environments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Test Room",
  "description": "My first environment"
}

###

### 4. Create session (paste environmentId from step 3)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/environments/PASTE_ENV_ID_HERE/sessions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "First Session"
}